OL,3,CWoman in court accused of killing
OL,4,Cchild by scalding her in bath in 1978
OL,6,FA 66-year-old woman has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt accused of killing a child by
OL,8,Fscalding her in a hot bath in 1978.
OL,10,FJanice Nix was charged on Tuesday over
OL,11,Fthe death of five-year-old Andrea
OL,12,FBernard, who was taken to hospital
OL,13,Fafter she suffered burns in Thornton
OL,14,FHeath, south London, on June 6 1978,
OL,15,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,17,FAndrea was treated at a hospital in
OL,18,FCroydon before being transferred to a
OL,19,Fspecialist burns unit in East
OL,20,FGrinstead, West Sussex, but died from
OL,21,Fher injuries on July 13 that year.
