OL,6,FThe defendant, of Rodenhurst Road,
OL,7,FClapham, south-west London, appeared
OL,8,Fat Uxbridge Magistrates' Court on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FThe court heard that on June 6 1978,
OL,12,FAndrea had been forced into a very hot
OL,13,Fbath which scalded 50% of her body.
OL,15,FNix is also accused of cruelty to
OL,16,Fanother child between October 1 1975
OL,17,Fand June 6 1978, when the child was
OL,18,Feight.
