OL,4,Cchild by scalding her in bath in 1978
OL,6,FThe defendant was aged between 16 and
OL,7,F19 at the time of the alleged
OL,8,Fincidents.
OL,10,FAt the short hearing, the 66-year-old
OL,11,Fspoke only to confirm her name, age
OL,12,Fand address.
OL,14,FNix wore a navy blue hoodie in the
OL,15,Fdock and was read the charges against
OL,16,Fher.
OL,18,FThe Metropolitan Police said the force
OL,19,Flaunched an investigation into
OL,20,FAndrea's death in September 2022.
