OL,6,FThe court heard the incident was
OL,7,Freported to police at that time by the
OL,8,Fother child, who is now an adult.
OL,10,FNix was freed on bail with conditions
OL,11,Fincluding to surrender her passports
OL,12,Fand not to travel to any international
OL,13,Ftravel hubs.
OL,15,FShe is set to appear at Isleworth
OL,16,FCrown Court on March 19.
